        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Whereby I may both clearly discern, and faithfully perform all the parts of my duty: for both these are spoken of in Scripture as the effects of a good understanding; and he that lives in the neglect of his duties, or the practice of wickedness, is called a ",
        "children": []
