        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "That I may discern between good and bad ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Namely, in causes and controversies among thy people; that I may not, through mistake, or prejudice, or passion, give wrong sentences, and call ",
        "children": []
      },
